        <p class="text">
        Find out what the World really thinks.<br><br>
        Fed up of "fake news"? Of being force fed "anaylsis" by self-appointed "experts"?<br>
        Ask your Question.<br>
        And see what the World really thinks.<br>
        <p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <div class="Log-in panel">
          Log in
        </div>
      
      <div class="sign-up panel">
        Sign up
      </div>  
    </div>



      
